Singles versus doubles isn't
in the spirit of the sports.

89
00:08:46,567 --> 00:08:49,267
He's here.

90
00:08:49,267 --> 00:08:50,267
Who are you?

91
00:08:50,267 --> 00:08:52,433
Oh, me?

92
00:08:52,433 --> 00:08:54,633
That guy's elder brother.

93
00:08:55,933 --> 00:08:58,033
You bastard.

94
00:09:04,333 --> 00:09:07,067
Oh, my.

95
00:09:08,867 --> 00:09:10,567
You're so late.

96
00:09:10,567 --> 00:09:12,533
