100
00:09:28,400 --> 00:09:32,500
Ju Yeon. Our Ju Yeon is here.

101
00:09:35,933 --> 00:09:38,067
It hurts. It hurts.

102
00:09:38,867 --> 00:09:40,467
Stop it, or you'll collapse.

103
