I'll report it to the police.

107
00:10:16,400 --> 00:10:20,767
That guy asked me to hit him!

108
00:10:38,267 --> 00:10:39,900
Did you get hit a lot?

109
00:10:39,900 --> 00:10:42,500
Is it your drinking habit
to get hit by someone?

110
00:10:42,500 --> 00:10:45,300
You're the first woman who saved me.

111
00:10:45,300 --> 00:10:48,100
Take me.

112
00:10:49,000 --> 00:10:52,300
Are we dating starting today?

113
