Player Lee Shin…

114
00:10:55,267 --> 00:10:57,833
Mr. Lee, please help…

115
00:10:58,967 --> 00:11:01,700
Are you sleeping? Now?

116
00:11:01,700 --> 00:11:04,567
Ah, right, the sedative.

117
00:11:04,567 --> 00:11:06,100
Are we dating starting today?

118
00:11:06,100 --> 00:11:08,200
- Starting today…
- Player Lee Shin.

119
00:11:08,200 --> 00:11:10,367
Mr. Lee!

120
00:11:15,600 --> 00:11:18,967
Oh, I don't know.

121
00:11:18,967 --> 00:11:22,200
I'll leave you both behind,
so do whatever you want.

122
00:11:22,200 --> 00:11:23,600
Got it?

123
00:11:23,600 --> 00:11:27,033
Oh, these brothers really drive me crazy.

124
00:11:27,567 --> 00:11:32,800
[Episode 9, True Love of First
Love and Unrequited Love]

125
00:11:34,200 --> 00:11:36,667
We are brothers.

126
00:11:36,667 --> 00:11:39,100
Have another drink!

127
00:11:50,867 --> 00:11:53,033
It's so hard.

128
00:11:53,033 --> 00:11:56,467
Hey, brothers.

129
00:11:57,500 --> 00:12:02,167
Come on. Get a grip.

130
00:12:04,033 --> 00:12:06,800
