145
00:14:15,000 --> 00:14:22,800
♫ The only thing that shines through is
that these things keep repeating themselves ♫

146
00:14:22,800 --> 00:14:29,333
♫ It's you ♫

147
00:14:31,200 --> 00:14:38,133
♫ It's you ♫

148
