me instead of his own brother.

226
00:20:47,367 --> 00:20:51,133
I have to give in to you. I heard
that you don't even go out to eat.

227
00:20:51,133 --> 00:20:52,467
Because you are worried that
you'll go out of the business.

228
00:20:52,467 --> 00:20:56,567
I thought that would be you.

229
00:20:56,567 --> 00:20:58,800
I heard that Cha Si On is causing trouble.

230
00:20:58,800 --> 00:21:02,100
Investors really hate when
something is not profitable.

231
00:21:08,700 --> 00:21:10,000
Ah, sir.

232
00:21:10,000 --> 00:21:11,933
CEO Hong.

233
00:21:11,933 --> 00:21:13,300
You already came out like this to greet me.

234
00:21:13,300 --> 00:21:14,967
Welcome.

235
00:21:14,967 --> 00:21:19,267
Thanks to Lee Shin's contract renewal,
the agency's image has also improved.

236
00:21:19,267 --> 00:21:22,367
It's all thanks to you, sir.

237
00:21:22,367 --> 00:21:24,567
- Let's go in.
- Yes.

238
00:21:24,567 --> 00:21:27,000
Mr. Lee, wait here.

239
00:21:31,700 --> 00:21:34,100
Jincheon Athletes' Village?

240
00:21:34,100 --> 00:21:37,033
You want me to go all the way
there and interpret for you?

241
00:21:37,033 --> 00:21:39,233
Yes.

242
00:21:39,233 --> 00:21:41,267
Yes, yes.

243
00:21:41,267 --> 00:21:44,000
Yes.

244
00:21:44,000 --> 00:21:49,300
It's a shame, but I'm sure you'll be able to
find another competent interpreter somewhere.

245
00:21:49,300 --> 00:21:50,900
Yes.

246
00:21:50,900 --> 00:21:53,167
Okay, then. Just hang up the phone now.

247
00:21:53,167 --> 00:21:55,867
I need to dig up the ground to drink beer.

248
00:21:57,467 --> 00:22:00,933
After clearing out all the beer in the fridge,

249
00:22:00,933 --> 00:22:02,767
beers come out of the ground.

250
00:22:02,767 --> 00:22:05,900
I should farm beer at our house.

251
00:22:05,900 --> 00:22:11,133
I had only put a few in
just to drink occasionally.

252
00:22:11,133 --> 00:22:12,600
Oh, ma'am…

253
00:22:12,600 --> 00:22:15,833
If you're going to just wander around
doing nothing, then just go back home.

254
00:22:15,833 --> 00:22:17,600
Why?

255
00:22:17,600 --> 00:22:19,533
Ma'am.

256
00:22:19,533 --> 00:22:22,867
Your mom is also insisting
to send you off quickly.

257
00:22:22,867 --> 00:22:27,033
I heard you went back and forth
to the countryside every day.

258
00:22:27,033 --> 00:22:30,500
What are you wandering around for?

259
00:22:30,500 --> 00:22:32,333
To the countryside…

260
00:22:32,333 --> 00:22:34,967
Oh, hold on. Hold on.

261
