559
00:42:46,267 --> 00:42:48,933
The view is nice.

560
00:42:53,633 --> 00:42:57,100
If I see a river, it's a river view.

561
00:42:57,100 --> 00:42:59,967
If I see the ocean, it's an ocean view.

562
00:42:59,967 --> 00:43:02,667
If I see Ju Yeon,

563
00:43:03,867 --> 00:43:06,300
I love you.

564
00:43:08,167 --> 00:43:11,967
What about the notebook? The emotion diary.

565
00:43:15,667 --> 00:43:19,400
Still, we have to eat the signature dish here.

566
00:43:19,400 --> 00:43:23,500
I've rented out this whole place, right?

567
00:43:28,433 --> 00:43:31,567
