15 years ago as if it was yesterday.

593
00:45:05,167 --> 00:45:08,167
I've missed her for a very long time.

594
00:45:08,167 --> 00:45:10,267
And finally, we've reunited.

595
00:45:10,267 --> 00:45:15,933
