598
00:45:27,833 --> 00:45:31,533
Even if I could go back to before I found her,

599
00:45:31,533 --> 00:45:33,600
I would gladly find her again.

600
00:45:33,600 --> 00:45:35,833
Willingly.

601
00:45:36,933 --> 00:45:41,033
Wow, I want this kind of guy.

602
00:45:42,700 --> 00:45:45,167
