651
00:49:21,100 --> 00:49:23,133
Well, that's a relief.

652
00:49:23,133 --> 00:49:26,333
He thinks you are his first love,

653
00:49:26,333 --> 00:49:29,400
so he might feel that way,

654
00:49:29,400 --> 00:49:32,267
but the true first love of my brother

655
00:49:32,267 --> 00:49:34,800
is not you.

656
00:49:39,500 --> 00:49:43,733
Yes, of course.

657
00:49:48,433 --> 00:49:50,767
Ju Yeon, try this.

658
00:49:52,833 --> 00:50:00,467
